name: Late Summer Horizon
description:
The breeze of late summer continues to blow forever in this art.

When you want to regain your composure, look at this art and you will feel at ease.

The delicate animation created without missing even one pixel is the love itself to wrap the viewer.
In addition, this animation uses a original unique technique. It creates a more realistic texture.
Pixel and real are fused, and a feeling of air is created there.

And dogs are not good at being hot.
